              |  #{docs.larger}
          .col-md-9.col-sm-8
            p
              | To increase icon sizes relative to their container, use the 
              code pe-lg
              |  (33% increase), 
              code pe-2x
              | ,
              code pe-3x
              | , 
              code pe-4x
              | , or 
              code pe-5x
              |  classes.
              br
              |  To align the icon at the middle of a text, use the 
              code pe-va
              |  class.
            pre
              code &lt;p&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;#{docs.larger} pe-lg pe-va&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; #{docs.larger}&lt;/p&gt;
